{"id":"concepts/protector-of-household","title":"Protector of the Household","type":"concepts","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Self-assigned role Yahir adopted during the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/alcoholism-in-the-family\">alcoholism</a> years — protecting <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/mom-yahir\">mom</a> and <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/emilio\">emilio</a> from dad's drunken episodes. Foundational identity frame in 2020 essays.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/alcoholism-in-the-family","label":"Alcoholism in the family"},{"id":"entities/emilio","label":"Emilio"},{"id":"entities/mom-yahir","label":"Mom (Yahir's mother)"}]}
